description:
Alif Laila ([i]The Arabian Nights[/i]) is a TV series based on the stories from [b]The Arabian Nights.[/b]
The Series starts right from the very beginning when [b]Scheherazade[/b] starts telling stories to [b]Shahryar[/b]. Alif Laila contains both the well-known and the lesser-known stories from [i]One Thousand and One Nights[/i] which are mentioned here. Actual word is "Alf Laila" meaning thousand nights.
